  ('medical-tech-moex-09511', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-105-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '病人有出血問題，其血小板凝集檢查結果如圖，則最可能之診斷為下列何者？（①加collagen，②加ADP，③加ristocetin）', '["Bernard Soulier syndrome", "Platelet storage pool disorder", "vWD", "Platelet-type vWD"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d3e1f3fe4aca", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d85823e84ddc", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105100", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第二次醫師牙醫師藥師分階段、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 46, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-09512', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-105-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於thrombotic thrombocytopenic purpura（TTP）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["可能由於ADAMTS13缺乏所造成的疾病", "Rituximab（Anti-CD20）對於TTP有不錯的療效", "病理切片最典型的發現是血管中出現vWF陽性的血栓", "先天及後天性TTP發生率各佔一半"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d3e1f3fe4aca", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d85823e84ddc", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105100", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第二次醫師牙醫師藥師分階段、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 47, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-09513', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-105-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於idiopathic thrombocytopenic purpura（ITP）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["急性ITP最常發生於2～6歲小孩", "小孩ITP常與病毒感染有關", "病人的抗體在固定補體反應（complement fixation）檢驗中呈陽性", "病人常見GPIIb/IIIa的抗體"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:37+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d3e1f3fe4aca", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d85823e84ddc", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105100", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第二次醫師牙醫師藥師分階段、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 48, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
